ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Back in my day, there was no bargaining! Prices are firm, you hear?!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Back in my day, there was no bargaining! Prices are firm, you hear?!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Before the crystals fell, this shop got a lot more business. Darn crystals!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Before the crystals fell, this shop got a lot more business. Darn crystals!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Are you going to buy anything, or just stand there looking like a fool?!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Are you going to buy anything, or just stand there looking like a fool?!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Don't even think about stealing! My telescopic eye is watching!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Don't even think about stealing! My telescopic eye is watching!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Hurry up and buy something, so I can enjoy my tea!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Hurry up and buy something, so I can enjoy my tea!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: You whippersnappers recognize quality, don't you?!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: You whippersnappers recognize quality, don't you?!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: My back is hurtin' again. I blame the crystals. Darn crystals!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: My back is hurtin' again. I blame the crystals. Darn crystals!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: You think I'm rude? Ha! My wife would have torn you a new one!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: You think I'm rude? Ha! My wife would have torn you a new one!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Who is that big purple fool? Zebra? Tell him to stop making a ruckus!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Who is that big purple fool? Zebra? Tell him to stop making a ruckus!

ShopkeeperDialog.SourceString: Out to save the world, are you? Well, what's taking you so long?!
ShopkeeperDialog.LocalizedString: Out to save the world, are you? Well, what's taking you so long?!

Text.SourceString: As long as you go into it with the right expectations it's not too bad, and more!
Text.LocalizedString: As long as you go into it with the right expectations it's not too bad, and more!

Text.SourceString: How doth the little crocodile Improve his shining tail, And pour the waters of the Nile On every golden scale!
Text.LocalizedString: How doth the little crocodile Improve his shining tail, And pour the waters of the Nile On every golden scale!
